⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Cmdr. Robert Iverson
node COR · COR · ⟦Cmdr. Robert Iverson:COR:e042c1⟧

WHO   — Cmdr. Robert Iverson — the first loss
WHAT  — The first of the terranauts to fall, whose death in a giant geode crystal cavern signals that this mission will cost the crew their lives.
WHERE — COR · The Core  Framework inputs: The Core (2003, dir. Jon Amiel)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because a disaster movie earns its stakes by spending a trusted veteran early — his loss is the promise that no one is safe.
HOW   — By command experience and the bad luck of the cavern that takes him, handing the controls to the younger pilot, Beck.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I led the descent and I was the first to fall — so you'd know, from then on, that none of us were promised the surface.

